If you want the spammers to go away, just report,  ignore, and FOCUS ON THE STREAM. Please.

It's not bad to have normies in the stream, it's actually good because they might become actual fans in the process. As long as they're respectful, I see nothing wrong with it. If they're not, you should just report and ignore. Avoid talking about it DURING the stream.

What I noticed were the Filipinos complaining about other Filipinos. They did it so much that they themselves became spams. I know that it's frustrating, but please, it would be better not to give them any attention at all. 

Now, we can't do anything about it anymore. It already happened. I just hope that what happened here serves as a lesson for everyone.

Edit: It breaks my heart thinking that she might've thought that that "Stop" comment was addressed to her. Imagine how it would feel if someone tells you to "stop" during your own live stream.
